               <msContents>
                  <summary>Vision of John, Son of Thunder, on the Dual Virginity of Mary; Forty-Nine Miracles of Mary, ተአምረ፡ ማርያም፡, Eight Miracles of Jesus, ተአምረ፡ ኢየሱስ፡</summary>
